messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

I want to commit myself to the things of true Godliness and I want to be released from the spirit of the world lust of eyes lust of the flesh and the pride of life I want to become a faithful husband and most importantly having a relationship with Jesus Christ

It's wonderful to hear your commitment to true godliness and your desire for a deeper relationship with Jesus Christ! We can certainly pray for you and support you in this journey. 

Here's a prayer you can use: 

"Heavenly Father, I come before you today through the blood of Jesus Christ. I pray against the spirit of lust, the lust of the eyes, the lust of the flesh, and the pride of life. I renounce all sexual sins and ask for your forgiveness. Help me to become a faithful husband and to grow in my relationship with You. Satisfy me with Your steadfast love and guide me in my pursuit of holiness. In Jesus' name, Amen."

If you need further support or resources, feel free to ask!
